com

Class AutoCompleteSearchHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.AutoCompleteSearchHandler

  • public class AutoCompleteSearchHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for turning a TextField node into a search bar based off the Jaro-Winkler distance. Also uses ListViews for viewing the results and selected restrictions.
    Author:
    Jagan Prem
    See Also:
    TextField, ListView
